lead_paragraph: Once again, the Minnesota Vikings will delay naming their starting quarterback until tomorrow’s pregame warm-ups. Tarvaris Jackson, who sustained a concussion last Sunday, was listed as questionable for the game at Green Bay. Brooks Bollinger will start if Jackson does not.
